column5: I have a parking coupon for "The Parking Spot" which is directly across the street from the Buffalo/Niagara International Airport....$7.59 per day or $49.95 per week plus tax and airport fee....if you can use it I'll send it to you....expires July 31st, 2012...FREE shuttle included of course.  http://www.theparkingspot.com/Locations/Locations.aspx?ID=52
Billy Bob, if the offer is still available, I would like to take you up on your generous offer. Will be flying out of Buffalo on March 23rd for a week.   Mike
Yep, I still have the one coupon sitting here.....it's yours....PM me your snail mail address.  Bob
A BIG THANK YOU to Billy Bob!!  Mike

It's on the way via the snail mail system....GOOD LUCK in VIVA LAS VEGAS....America's Adult Playground....we'll be there a couple of weeks after you guys....don't break the casinos before we get there....LOL...
BTW.....are there any more that would be interested in these coupons....I get them in the mail every so often.  Bob
I guess you know what junk mail to keep.  :-)
Sir, coupons are NOT junk mail in my house....that's a very serious matter around here....  "I have a COUPON"....who said that in Seinfeld ? ? ?
